his own brain surgery.

00:00:44.977 --> 00:00:46.346 align:start size:53% position:47%
Morning, morning.

00:00:46.446 --> 00:00:51.217 align:start size:91% position:9% line:88%
<i> (Jaye)
 Daniel Meadows still has
 moments of total disbelief.</i>

