00:01:00.360 --> 00:01:01.427 align:start size:13% position:88%
Now?

00:01:01.527 --> 00:01:04.063 align:start size:91% position:9% line:78%
One.

00:01:01.527 --> 00:01:04.063 align:start size:63% position:38%
Great.
Give me a big smile.

