 Makes conversation.</i>

00:05:44.543 --> 00:05:45.644 align:start size:66% position:34% line:0%
Did you go to school?

00:05:45.744 --> 00:05:47.580 align:start size:78% position:22% line:0%
Where'd you go to school?

00:05:45.744 --> 00:05:47.580 align:start position:0% line:14%
Yeah.

00:05:48.948 --> 00:05:50.516 align:start size:75% position:25% line:0%
<i> (Jaye)
 Counts backwards.</i>

