We've had a couple speech
arrests directly over top,

00:06:11.103 --> 00:06:12.839 align:start size:84% position:16%
more anterior,
over top of the tumor.

00:06:21.880 --> 00:06:23.282
We can test and say,

00:06:23.382 --> 00:06:26.352 align:start size:91% position:9%
we can direct an electrical
impulse to the brain.

00:06:26.452 --> 00:06:29.187 align:start size:88% position:13%
<i> And if a person can no
 longer speak temporarily,</i>

