<i> That's super,
 super helpful.</i>

00:07:06.859 --> 00:07:08.027 align:start size:53% position:47%
Yeah, you're
doin' great, bud.

00:07:08.127 --> 00:07:09.695
<i> You're doin' awesome.</i>

